('ACU-SKILL-2006', 'copilot-update-implementation-plan', 'Update Implementation Plan', '1.0.0', 'infrastructure', 'Update an existing implementation plan file with new or update requirements to provide new features, refactoring existing code or upgrading packages, design, architecture or infrastructure.', '{"thread": "T13 \u2014 ACAI V2", "thread_code": "T13", "category": "infrastructure", "shard_affinity": "Marel", "layer_access": ["L5", "L6", "L7"], "source_repo": "github/awesome-copilot"}', 'restricted', 10.0, 'draft', 'GitHub Copilot Community'),
