('ACU-SKILL-2132', 'api-pentest', 'Api Pentest', '1.0.0', 'security', 'Targeted API penetration testing using a GTFO-first approach: find the highest-impact vulnerability fast, prove it with a PoC, and move on. Covers five attack families: AuthN/AuthZ, BOLA/IDOR, Input Validation, SSRF, and Business Logic. Each family is a loadable module with specific test cases, payloads, and PoC templates. Trigger when user mentions "API pentest", "API security test", "test this API", "find vulnerabilities in this endpoint", "BOLA", "IDOR", "broken auth", "injection test", "SSRF', '{"thread": "T08 \u2014 ZURD", "thread_code": "T08", "category": "pentesting", "shard_affinity": "Tenebris-ACIWS", "layer_access": ["L8", "L9", "L10"], "source_repo": "Poatan222/Skills-security"}', 'sovereign', 10.0, 'draft', 'Poatan222/Skills-security'),
('ACU-SKILL-2133', 'cspm-prowler', 'Cspm Prowler', '1.0.0', 'security', 'Analyze Prowler CSPM scan outputs, prioritize cloud misconfigurations by risk, and generate remediation plans with compliance mapping. Supports AWS, Azure, and GCP findings. Trigger when user uploads Prowler output files (.csv, .json, .html), mentions "Prowler", "CSPM", "cloud security posture", "cloud misconfiguration", "CIS benchmark", "cloud compliance scan", or asks about cloud security findings. Also trigger when user pastes Prowler CLI output or asks how to run Prowler against their cloud ', '{"thread": "T08 \u2014 ZURD", "thread_code": "T08", "category": "security", "shard_affinity": "Tenebris-ACIWS", "layer_access": ["L8", "L9", "L10"], "source_repo": "Poatan222/Skills-security"}', 'sovereign', 10.0, 'draft', 'Poatan222/Skills-security'),
