('ACU-SKILL-2173', 'frontend-design-review', 'Frontend Design Review', '1.0.0', 'security', 'Review and create distinctive, production-grade frontend interfaces with high design quality and design system compliance. Evaluates using three pillars: frictionless insight-to-action, quality craft, and trustworthy building. USE FOR: PR reviews, design reviews, accessibility audits, design system compliance checks, creative frontend design, UI code review, component reviews, responsive design checks, theme testing, and creating memorable UI. DO NOT USE FOR: Backend API reviews, database schema', '{"thread": "T08 \u2014 ZURD", "thread_code": "T08", "category": "security", "shard_affinity": "Tenebris-ACIWS", "layer_access": ["L8", "L9", "L10"], "source_repo": "microsoft/skills"}', 'sovereign', 10.0, 'draft', 'Microsoft'),
