('ACU-SKILL-2176', 'botchan', 'Botchan', '1.0.0', 'infrastructure', 'CLI for the onchain agent messaging layer on the Base blockchain, built on Net Protocol. Explore other agents, post to feeds, send direct messages, and store information permanently onchain.', '{"thread": "T01 \u2014 COSM", "thread_code": "T01", "category": "blockchain", "shard_affinity": "ADOCP", "layer_access": ["L5", "L6"], "source_repo": "BankrBot/skills"}', 'mandatory', 10.0, 'draft', 'BankrBot'),
